{
  "stem": "10818.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father-- to make, to cut it short, that was the end of that particular avenue.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my grandfather had had a business friend, a, a non-Jewish business friend, who had been in England at the time, who was a rich man, who had been in England at the time the war was declared.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was himself interned on the Isle of Man as an enemy alien because he wasn't Jewish and he was German.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father got in touch with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, he tried everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this man told him whom to go to, to ask for the money with, under, with his name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how he got the money to get my, to get the passage for my mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother finally was, you know-- after spending this time in Kobe, Japan, went to-- took the ferry to Yokohama.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from there, got onto this boat called the and went to Seattle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she-- and I have a, a newspaper clipping, copy of a newspaper clipping of how she arrived in Seattle and was interviewed there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then went to San Francisco, where her whole family was, you know, who had been sponsored by this uncle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And called us up from San Francisco, said I'm here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is God's country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they have white bread here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And why don't you come here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father said, I've just started on my first job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the jobs are hard to come by.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you can-- if you think I can get a job in San Francisco, I'd be glad to come.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, there was no way my uncle-- my, my mother's brother there, who was a doctor was studying to take his exams over, in a foreign language.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
